{"tid":2372740,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Red Velvet Irene&申承浩主演電影《Double Patty》都市唯美追夢預告公開！","createTime":"2021-01-20T02:46:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-20T17:00:25.000Z","uid":16659,"like":15,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"6ba733a9202d068b2026f9ec34a765da24f79688","tid":2372740,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T02:46:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_7a9bfb3bb4c5f75ff049a2977cee6e45/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-19/133122-894074.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_7a9bfb3bb4c5f75ff049a2977cee6e45%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-19%2F133122-894074.jpg&h=1fcc57f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nIrene 首次挑戰電影演技，搭檔《18歲的瞬間》的高挑暖男申承浩，預告看了讓人覺得很賞心悅目啊～！<br />\n<br />\n人氣女團 Red Velvet 的 Irene（裴柱現）與申承浩攜手主演的全新都市電影《Double Patty》公開了首波預告，預計在2月份正式推出，預告中滿滿的亮點和全新 CP 組合也讓人非常期待。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_de7fa9ee31a66a9f5f246d5a2e29c3cf/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-19/133122-894075.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_de7fa9ee31a66a9f5f246d5a2e29c3cf%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-19%2F133122-894075.jpg&h=392a8f27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n電影《Double Patty》講述摔角界的潛力股－宇藍（申承浩 飾）和夢想成為主播的志願生－賢智（Irene 飾）相遇後，互相為對方加油、給予彼此力量的成長故事。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_0d9139df393d3e43e56d18305594125f/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-19/133122-894076.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_0d9139df393d3e43e56d18305594125f%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-19%2F133122-894076.jpg&h=ff2e3643&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_d02524a4f479e504829aae41908a80cf/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-19/133122-894077.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_d02524a4f479e504829aae41908a80cf%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-19%2F133122-894077.jpg&h=2d687050&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▼預告中，兩位追夢的青年在兼職與求職的同時，每天都在忙碌中渡過，時間的流逝和對未來的不安感襲來，在追夢的過程中默默成為彼此的力量，背景音樂由 Irene 和申承浩一起合唱，也增加了電影的融入感：「走吧！」、「一起嗎？」、「嗯，一起走吧！」<br />\n<a href=\"https://tv.naver.com/v/17998979\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftv.naver.com%2Fv%2F17998979&d=CthjHxCXz%2Bl0vOF3eBkmegqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=7a28dfd7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tv.naver.com/v/17998979</a><br />\n<br />\n▼Irene的高顏值配上申承浩的養眼好身材～<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_a342ab7582160f159b6a3b8d1c2377bf/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-19/133122-894078.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_a342ab7582160f159b6a3b8d1c2377bf%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-19%2F133122-894078.jpg&h=c07c0b91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《Double Patty》將會在2月份正式上映。"},{"pid":"a328651239443d17a12ffbed7524e185867f0528","tid":2372740,"uid":93096,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T02:48:13.000Z","msg":"支持Irene...！!"},{"pid":"64dff1a0db36c13133d89bb2c9d9dc580dc296d0","tid":2372740,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T02:50:03.000Z","msg":"男主角好7呀"},{"pid":"0fcf83df2e4c8c04c597c3b6a48e8906a75dccac","tid":2372740,"uid":205928,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T02:57:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />irene"},{"pid":"99e3cfa805543aa328272712cb13e69a90705aaa","tid":2372740,"uid":261849,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T03:01:35.000Z","msg":"條女又幾正喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br /